""" tests for the file finder """
assert utils.find_file('anything', []) is None
assert utils.find_file('anything', ['tests/templates']) is None
assert utils.find_file('auth', ['tests/templates']) is None
assert utils.find_file('index.html', 'tests/templates'
    ) == 'tests/templates/index.html'
assert utils.find_file('index.html', ('tests/templates',
    'tests/templates/auth')) == 'tests/templates/index.html'
assert utils.find_file('index.html', ('tests/templates/auth',
    'tests/templates')) == 'tests/templates/auth/index.html'
